parameters:
One day... a boy arrived at an orphanage in the forest, run
by a young woman.

After settling her husband's funeral, who had died of an
epidemic, the boy's mother fell for a younger man and
eventually, the two of them disappeared from the boy's life.

The boy who was admitted to the orphanage eventually stopped
speaking to anyone, never opened his closed heart, and day
after day, gripped his sword, pushing his small body to its
limits.

The woman worried about the boy who wouldn't interact with
others or open his heart to anyone, and she spoke to him
whenever there was an opportunity.

However... it was all in vain for the woman. Still, the boy
did not attempt to open his closed heart.
One day, a band of fugitives appeared at the orphanage.

This place, standing in the midst of the forest, seemed like
the perfect hideout for them.

The bandits took the women and children hostage and
barricaded themselves in the orphanage.

In exchange for the children's lives, a woman offered her
virginity to them.

After undergoing even more intense training that pushed his
body and mind to the limit, the boy returned to this place
once again.

The hideout, now overtaken by bandits, held no
sentimentality for the boy with thirsty eyes.
Waiting for nightfall, the boy infiltrated the orphanage.

The darkness inside the building was no obstacle for him,
who had once lived in this place.
